SHELL PETROLEUM CORPORATION v. Ruth E. EVANS. No. 354. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Sept. 9, 1930. Allen, Underwood & Canterbury, of Tulsa, Okl., for appellant. Charles H. Ruth, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, PHILLIPS, and McDERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed at appellant’s costs September 9, 1930, on motion of appellant.
